general

Class IndexControllerD

  • java.lang.Object
    • general.IndexControllerD

  • public class IndexControllerD
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used as our index giving users access to their respective actions in our system. Each action (ordering food for example) gets loaded inside a pane in the index controller screen This screen is different for each user according to their types in our DB
    Since:
    01.01.2022
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    dorin bahar
